definitions.definition: A nipple -like protuberance on a part or organ of the body.

subdefinitions.definition: A vascular process of connective tissue extending into and nourishing the root of a hair , feather , or developing tooth .
Any of the vascular protuberances of the dermal layer of the skin extending into the epidermal layer and often containing tactile corpuscles .
Any of the small protuberances on the upper surface of the tongue often containing taste buds .

definitions.definition: A small fleshy projection on a plant .

main_definition: ( anatomy ) A nipple -like protuberance on a part or organ of the body.
secondary_definitions: ( botany ) A small fleshy projection on a plant .
